<div class="title">Only one SSL certificate for the domain</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>A domain can only have one SSL certificate.
Example: If your domain already has an SSL certificate and you order a new one, then the new certificate will overwrite the existing one.</p>
</div>
</td>
