<h2 id="1300">4. Renewing an SSL certificate</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You will be notified shortly before your SSL certificate expires.
The notification includes further information and instructions.
But you can always see for yourself when your SSL certificate expires and if your certificate will be renewed automatically.</p>
</div>
<div class="imageblock">
<div class="content">
